@startuml
' Onion architecture overview for Traders Mirror
skinparam dpi 150
skinparam shadowing false
left to right direction

actor "User / Browser" as User

package "Presentation\n(React UI)" as P #DDDDFF {
  [TradeJournal]
  [TradeDetail]
  [Settings]
}

package "Application\n(Use-Cases / Services)" as A #CCEEFF {
  [TradeService]
  [AnalysisService]
}

package "Domain\n(Entities / Value Objects)" as D #AAEEFF {
  [Trade]
  [TradeFactory]
  [ValueObjects\n(TradeSymbol, EntryDate, Size, Price, Side)]
}

package "Infrastructure\n(Adapters / Repos)" as I #EECCCC {
  [InMemoryTradeRepository]
  [LocalStorageSettings]
}

' interactions
User -> P : interact
P --> A : calls use-cases
A --> D : uses factories/entities
A --> I : calls repository adapters (ports -> adapters)
I --> D : persists primitives

note left of A
  Application layer orchestrates
  domain logic and repositories
end note

note right of D
  Domain contains typed
  Value Objects and Domain Errors
end note

@enduml
